To convert from FZJ to ICBM directory structure, use the
provided script fzj2icbm.ksh

To convert form ICBM to FZJ directory sturcture, use the
provided script icbm2fzj.ksh

Otherwise, you need to adjust the glues path (where GLUES is installed
on your system) and the SiSi path (where SiSi is installed on your
system) manually.

Files that need to be adjusted are given below

./simulations/*.sce
./simulations/*.sim
./simulations/README
./Makefile
./src/Makefile

